**Location**: `/workspace/modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/credit/CdsTrancheTradeCalculationFunction.java`

**Purpose**: Wires CDS tranche trades into Strata's scenario calculation engine

**Implementation**:
